nt\"><p>The 2019 Apple AirPods provide you with even more talk time and voice-activated Siri access. Just take the AirPods out of the case to activate them – music will start playing the moment you put the AirPods in your ears and will handily pause when you remove them.</p> \n \n\n<p><strong>H1 chip </strong><br>\nApple’s H1 chip ensures your 2019 AirPods will have even better connectivity, will increase battery life and also speed up pairing times. It also provides lower gaming latency and voice-enabled Siri access.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Ask Siri</strong><br>\nIf you want Apple’s voice assistant to help out, just say: ‘Hey Siri’ and it will spring into action, meaning you no longer have to reach for your iPhone.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Power up</strong><br>\nJust use the trusty Lightning port to charge the case. To check the battery levels, just ask Siri: ‘How’s the battery on my AirPods?’</p>\n\n<p><strong>Clear sounds</strong><br>\nWhen you’re on a call or talking to Siri, the AirPods’ speech-detecting accelerometer works with beamforming microphones to filter out background noise and focus on the sound of your voice.</p> \n\n<p><strong>Use your way</strong><br>\nThere are times when using just one AirPod seems sensible – not to worry, you can wear one or both. Additionally, you can play or skip forward with a double tap when listening to music.</p>\n\n<p>These AirPods work with compatible iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple Watch, Apple TV and iPod models.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnl