standard-pdp-ui\" modalrootid=\"page-root\" accordion=\"true\" displaytitle=\"false\" experiments=\"\" isbrandpromiseactive=\"true\"></jl-reviews></div></div></details>','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/238086343?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','APPLE'),(101,'Apple AirPods Pro (2nd generation) with MagSafe Charging Case (USB-C) 2023','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->86184815</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Apple\'s 2nd iteration of the AirPods Pro really are just that: Pro. Fitted with Active Noise Cancellation and Adaptive Transparency to block out unwanted noise, Spatial Audio makes a welcome return for a more personal listening experience. Touch controls now let you adjust volume with a swipe, and the six-hour battery life means you\'re free to listen, chat and experience for as long as you like.</p>\n\n<p><b>Please be aware:</b>\nThe AirPods Pro include a USB-C charging cable, but do not include a USB-C power adapter. Therefore, if you do not already own one, you will need to purchase the <b>Apple 20W USB-C Power Adapter</b> in order to charge these AirPods.</p>\n\n<p><b>Active Noise Cancellation</b><br>\nFeaturing up to two times more noise cancellation than their predecessor, the H2-powered AirPods Pro are built to let you listen in peace.</p>\n\n<p><b>A perfect fit</b><br>\nNow with an extra small size, four pairs of silicone tips are included to fit a wider range of ears. The tips create an acoustic seal that closes in the sound - and secure AirPods Pro in place.</p>\n\n<p><b>Hear what you want</b><br>\nAdaptive Transparency harnesses the power of H2 to minimise the intensity of loud noises like sirens or power tools — so you can comfortably hear the world around you.</p>\n\n<p><b>A higher level of control</b><br>\nTouch control lets you easily manage playback functions from the stem. Swipe up or down to adjust volume, press to play and pause music or answer and end calls, or hold to switch between Active Noise Cancellation and Adaptive Transparency.</p>\n\n<p><b>Sound tuned to you</b><br>\nPersonalised Spatial Audio with dynamic head tracking immerses you deeper in all-around-you sound. And Adaptive EQ accounts for the fit of AirPods Pro, so you hear every frequency just as it was intended.\n\n</p><p><b>H2 chip</b><br>\nApple\'s new H2 chip is the force behind AirPods Pro and their advanced audio performance. It works in concert with a custom‑built driver and amplifier to deliver crisp, clear high notes and deep, rich bass in stunning definition — so every sound is more vivid than ever.\n\n</p><p><b>A case of unmistakable power</b><br>\nAirPods Pro are now easier to find than its predecessors. The headphones themselves play a chime when dropped outside of the case, and the case now has a speaker that\'ll play a louder sound when prompted by the Find My app.</p>\n\n<p>These AirPods work with compatible iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple Watch, Apple TV and iPod models.</p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-descripti