oduct:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89711303</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Sony’s CH520 headphones are ideal for all-day listening. Letting you enjoy your music without the wires, they connect to Bluetooth devices (up to two at the same time), and last for up to a huge fifty hours off one charge. You can take crystal-clear phone calls with the built-in mic, and they stay comfortable over the longer listen.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Multipoint Bluetooth</strong><br>\nEnjoy the benefit of unrestricted listening and disconnect from the need for cables with Bluetooth. Just pair the WH-CH520 with your smart device, with no wires in sight ...or getting in the way. With Multipoint connection, they can pair with up to two devices, and switch easily between them, and they support Fast Pair and Swift Pair with compatible Android and Windows devices.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Long listening</strong><br>\nRecharging via USB cable, the battery lasts for up to a whopping 50 hours to keep you immersed in music all day …and beyond. And when you do run low and need to get going, a quick three-minute charge will give you one and a half hours of playback.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Super Sony sound</strong><br>\nSony’s Digital Sound Enhancement Engine (DSEE) restores digital music files closer to their original recording quality, while 360 Reality Audio Certified presents an all-round more immersive listen. Plus, you can personalise your sound settings in the Sony Headphones Connect app.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Super clear calls</strong><br>\nPhone calls on these Sony wireless headphones are always crystal-clear, thanks to the brand’s noise suppression technology.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Stay comfortable</strong><br>\nWith an adjustable headband, soft earpads, and a lightweight design, they stay comfortable, even over longer 