cordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"\"><jl-reviews data-testid=\"product:reviews\" productid=\"5287554\" producturl=\"/apple-airpods-max-noise-cancelling-wireless-bluetooth-over-ear-headphones/p5287554\" apikey=\"AIzaSyDrfSLzq-WxgyLPSKu53oW7y4TJo7bQdpY\" clientid=\"standard-pdp-ui\" modalrootid=\"page-root\" accordion=\"true\" displaytitle=\"false\" experiments=\"\" isbrandpromiseactive=\"true\"></jl-reviews></div></div></details>','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/239753454?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','APPLE'),(106,'Beats Studio Buds True Wireless Bluetooth In-Ear Headphones with Active Noise Cancelling, Black','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined ProductAccordion_accordionWithKeyFeatures__zS4LS\" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>YES</dd><dt>Noise Reduction or Cancelling<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Active Noise Cancellation</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>53g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>True Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89731113</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Beats\' Studio Buds have been engineered to deliver powerful, balanced audio in a compact design. They feature two distinct listening modes: Active Noise Cancelling (ANC), to continuously block unwanted outside noise, as well as Transparency mode, for those times when you need to be aware of the world around you. Compatible with both Apple and Android devices, these True Wireless ear-buds deliver the renowned sound of Beats with ergonomic style, comfort, and all-day rechargeable power.</p>\n \n \n \n <p><strong>Listening modes </strong><br> \n \n Beats Studio Buds enable you to have total control of your sound. Active Noise Cancelling (ANC) blocks unwanted outside noise using a finely-tuned filter that dynamically adapts to your surroundings. Transparency mode is just a button press away, for those times when you need to hear travel announcements. Handily, the external-facing microphones mix the sounds of your surroundings back in with your music for a natural, \'open\' listening experience.</p>\n \n \n \n <p><strong>Clear sound </strong><br>\n \n Beats Studio Buds\' dual-element diaphragm driver resides within a two-chamber housing, resulting in clear sound with outstanding stereo separation. Their advanced digital processor then optimises audio performance for loudness and clarity, whilst simultaneously ensuring clean noise-cancellation.</p>\n \n \n \n <p><strong>Power up </strong><br>\n \n With up to 8 hours of listening time with two additional charges – provided by their pocket-sized charging case, Beats Studio Buds can offer up to 24 hours of combined playback. If you need a cheeky top up, a 5-minute Fast Fuel charging gives up to 1 hour of playback when the battery is low. </p>\n \n <p><strong>Compatible with Apple &amp; Android</strong><br>\n These Beats ear-buds work with both Android and iOS devices, connecting via a super stable Bluetooth connection.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Call me </strong><br>\n \n Beats Studio Buds\' dual-beam forming microphones target your voice and filter out wind and external noise for high quality call performance and elevated voice clarity. Additionally, on-ear controls allow you to manage calls and control music. You\'re even able to customise the “Press and Hold” function to work for either ANC or your voice assistant.</p>\n \n \n \n <p><strong> Customised fit </strong><br>\n \n The three (included) soft, silicone eartip sizes (small, medium, or large) give you a customised fit and will help to create an acoustic seal for an even more immersive listening experience. </p>\n \n <p><em>These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p></div><ul data-testid=\"description:links\" class=\"DescriptionLinks_descriptionLinks__AHNFv\"><li><a data-testid=\"description:links:link\" href=\"/buying-guides/headphones-buying-guide\">Headphones Buying Guide</a></li></ul></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex