el__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Yes - 5.0</dd><dt>Noise Reduction or Cancelling<!-- -->:</dt><dd>No Noise Cancellation</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>90g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>True Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89733108</strong></p><ul data-testid=\"description:icons\" class=\"DescriptionIcons_icons___QNTd\"><li class=\"DescriptionIcons_icon__9StwT\"><span class=\"DescriptionIcons_text__SalR_\" data-testid=\"description:icons:text\">What Hi*Fi? Awards 2022</span><img class=\"DescriptionIcons_image__5HCJi\" data-testid=\"description:icons:image\" src=\"https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/whathifi-award-wirelessearbudsunder100-181022\" alt=\"\"></li></ul><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>The WF-C500 in-ear headphones combine truly wireless freedom with super Sony sound. They’re ideal for sports and active lifestyles, with an ergonomic design to stay super-comfortable and they’re water and sweat resistant, so are ideal wireless sports headphones, great for running and even your workouts in the gym, so you can keep on moving to the music.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Truly wireless listening</strong><br>\nWith two independent ear-buds fitting comfortably and securely in your ears, not a single wire gets in your way. Feel the inspiring freedom of truly wire-free listening.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Small and light</strong><br>\nDesigned small, these ear buds fit securely and comfortably in your ears. The lightweight, smooth rounded shape makes them a pleasure to wear, leaving you free to focus on what matters: your music.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Ideal for sports with IPX4 splash and sweat resistance</strong><br>\nThese earbuds are also IPX4-rated water and sweat resistant so are ideal wireless sports headphones, great for running and even your workouts in the gym.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Delightful listening</strong><br>\nWith Sony\'s Digital Sound Enhancement Engine (DSEE), high frequency sound and fine fade-out sound, musical tracks are restored for a more authentic listening experience. You can also tailor music to your own taste using the EQ setting on the Sony Headphones Connect app.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Stable Bluetooth connectivity</strong><br>\nA Bluetooth headphones chip, which transmits sound to the left and right Bluetooth earbuds simultaneously, coupled with an optimised antenna design, ensures a stable connection and outstanding listening. Low audio latency makes for enjoyable viewing too. The Fast Pair feature for Android and Swift Pair feature for Windows 10 makes it quick and easy to pair your WF-C500 with your devices via Bluetooth.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Listen all day, charge in minutes</strong><br>\nAt full charge, these Sony true wireless headphones offer 10 hours of power, while the handy charging case provides an extra 10 hours. That means a full 20 hours of listening every time you leave the house. And if you need to top up in a hurry, a quick 10 minute charge gives you up to 60 minutes of play time.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Voice assistant compatibility</strong><br>\nThe WF-C500 work with Google Assist