ccordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89730414</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Jlab Audio\'s Go Air Pop are smaller and lighter than the brand\'s Go Air earbuds, but just as great on-the-go. With a perfectly pocket-sized slim charging case, they pack a powerful audio punch. Featuring touch control, and, with Dual Connect, each earbud can be used independently. You can take phone calls with ease, and they last for a total of 32 hours playing time.</p>\n \n <p><strong>True wireless freedom</strong><br>\n With two independent earbuds fitting comfortably and securely in your ears, not a single wire gets in your way. Connect wirelessly with your smart device via a high-quality, stable Bluetooth connection.</p>\n \n <p><strong>JLab Audio sound</strong><br>\n Enjoy rich and crisp JLab Audio quality sound with 6mm drivers. And, with just a tap on their touch sensors, you can tune to your preference with three EQ settings; Signature, Balanced, and Bass Boost, all without an app.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Dual connect</strong><br>\n The Go Air Pop connect automatically to your device once paired, and you’ll get a seamless connection, whether you’re using the earbuds independently or together. And you can take phone calls with ease with the built-in mic in either earbud.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Comfortable &amp; durable</strong><br>\n Three sets of gel-tip sizes let you find the ideal fit with a secure in-ear seal, and they\'re IPX4 rated splash resistant. The Go Air Pop are 15% smaller than the brand’s Go Air, so are ideal for smaller ears, and 40% lighter including the carry case, for super portability.</p>\n \n<p><strong>32 hour battery life</strong><br>\nThey last for up to 8 hours off a single charge, with the power for an additional 24 hours in the included pocket-sized charging carry case. Recharge the case easily with the integrated charging cable.</p>\n \n <p><em>These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accor