d=\"standard-pdp-ui\" modalrootid=\"page-root\" accordion=\"true\" displaytitle=\"false\" experiments=\"\" isbrandpromiseactive=\"true\"></jl-reviews></div></div></details>','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/239876665?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','MARSHALL'),(112,'Sony WF-C700N Noise Cancelling True Wireless Bluetooth In-Ear Headphones with Mic/Remote, Black','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89733113</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>The WF-C700N ear-buds from Sony combine truly wireless freedom, superb Sony sound, and the full-on focus afforded by Noise Cancellation. Glorious. They’re ideal for sports and active lifestyles, with an ergonomic design to stay super-comfortable and they’re water and sweat resistant, so are ideal wireless sports headphones, great for running and even your workouts in the gym, so you can keep on moving to the music.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Truly wireless listening</strong><br>\nWith two independent ear-buds fitting comfortably and securely in your ears, not a single wire gets in your way. Feel the inspiring freedom of truly wire-free listening.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Digital Noise Cancelling with Ambient Sound Mode</strong><br>\nDigital Noise Cancelling blocks out the distraction of external sound so you can focus on maximising your music. Or choose Ambient Mode to mix your music and the sound of your surroundings so you can stay safely aware.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Ideal for sports with IPX4 splash and sweat resistance</strong><br>\nThese earbuds are also IPX4-rated water and sweat resistant so are ideal wireless sports headphones, great for running and even your workouts in the gym.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Ergonomic comfort</strong><br>\nThey’ve been designed with your comfort in mind, featuring an ergonomic surface design that perfectly matches the ear for a more stable fit.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Super Sony sound</strong><br>\nSony’s Digital Sound Enhancement Engine (DSEE) restores digital music files closer to their original recording quality, while 360 Reality Audio Certified presents a more immersive listening. Plus, you can personalise your sound settings in the Sony Headphones Connect app.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Super clear calls</strong><br>\nPhone calls on these Sony wireless headphones are always crystal-clear, thanks to the brand’s Wind Noise Reduction Structure tech.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Listen all day, charge in minutes</strong><br>\nAt full charge, these Sony true wireless headphones offer 10 hours of power, while the handy charging case provides an extra 10 hours. That means a full 20 hours of listening every time you leave the house. And if you need to top up in a hurry, a quick 10 minute charge gives you up to 60 minutes of play time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:de