Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>YES</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>18.6g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89721114</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Beats Flex wireless earphones bring the renowned sound of Beats, with a versatility to suit modern life. Magnetic earbuds play the music automatically when they\'re in your ears, and pause it when they’re attached around your neck (compatible iOS required*). A Flex-form cable and a choice of ear-tip sizes ensure all-day comfort to match their all-day battery, and they stay tangle-free thanks to those magnetic buds.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Beats audio</strong><br>\nFlex deliver the renowned Beats sound: rich and powerful audio that keeps you going all day. Dual chamber acoustic design and a layered driver produce outstanding stereo separation, together with full and precise bass, and clear and crisp mids and highs. Advanced processing fine-tunes the sound for an emotive listening experience.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Class 1 Bluetooth</strong><br>\nA Class 1 Bluetooth connection means extended range and fewer dropouts, and an advanced built-in mic reduces wind noise for calls from your smart phone. Manage playback, take calls and activate your smart voice assistant with in-line controls.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Apple W1 Chip</strong><br>\nThe Apple W1 chip can integrate the Beats Flex with any other Apple products you may have, so you can seamlessly switch between devices that are synced to iCloud (requires iCloud account and macOS Sierra, iOS 10, watchOS 3 or later versions). And you can use one-tap Audio Sharing to sync with other selected compatible Beats headphones or Apple AirPods, to wirelessly share what you’re listening to with others.</p>\n\n<p><strong>All-day charge</strong><br>\nBeats Flex last for up to 12 hours of listening, so they’ll keep going all day. And if you get low on power, a quick 10-minute Fast Fuel charge gives you an hour and a half of power.</p><br>\n\n<p><em>*compatible with iOS and iPadOS 14 or later, macOS 11 or later, watchOS 7 or later, and tvOS 14 or later</em></p></div><ul data-testid=\"description:links\" class=\"DescriptionLinks_descriptionLinks__AHNFv\"><li><a data-testid=\"description:links:link\" href=\"/buying-guides/headphones-buying-guide\">Headphones Buying Guide</a></li></ul></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>