accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89710302</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>The Bose Headphones 700 combine excellent wireless audio, controllable noise cancellation, easy access to voice assistants, and superior call quality. So you can get the most out of your smart phone while it stays in your pocket. They’re built for all-day listening comfort with premium design and a long battery life.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Personalise your noise cancellation</strong><br>\n With eleven levels of noise cancellation, you can personalise your listening to adjust the level of exterior noise that you hear. Adjust it between full blocking of distractions to no noise cancellation at all. Or, for a quick pause or chat to someone nearby, press the button for Conversation Mode to briefly let surrounding noise in.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Bose sound quality</strong><br>\n Enjoy renowned Bose sound quality with signature active EQ and impressive bass response. At both low and high volume they provide a lush, immersive and detailed listening experience.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Adaptive mic system</strong><br>\n Phone calls are clear, even in noisy environments. A four-microphone system isolates your voice while cancelling the noise around you so you can hear and be heard at all times.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Optimised for your voice assistant</strong><br>\n The Bose Headphones 700 are optimised for both Google Assistant and Alexa. Select your chosen voice assistant within the Bose Music app (available on iOS and Android) and activate with a press of the dedicated button on the right ear-cup to activate voice assistance with music, navigation, weather, and more.*</p>\n \n <p><strong>Bose comfort</strong><br>\n The Bose 700 are designed for all-day comfort, constructed from synthetic protein leather they’re both soft but durable. And they’ll last for up to 20 hours off a single charge.</p>\n \n <p><strong>Simple, intuitive controls</strong><br>\n Manage volume, calls, and music just by touching the earcup.</p>\n \n <p><strong>When your home is your office</strong><br>\n They’re great for both listening to music when working in your home office, and for making phone calls with high quality audio when needing to listen or communicate clearly. Powerful noise cancelling, astonishing sound and superior voice pick-up all combine to create an ideal business companion. </p>\n \n <p><strong>Bose Music App</strong><br>\n Use the Bose Music app on your iOS or Android mobile device to control sound settings and music selection, and to ensure your Bose smart products work together.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Optimised for Bose SimpleSync</strong><br>\nThis product is optimised for Bose SimpleSync. With SimpleSync technology, you can pair it with selected Bose speakers and soundbars for a personalised listening experience.</p>\n\n\n<p><em>* Voice services (Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant) may vary and may not be available in all languages and countries or on all platforms (Apple iOS and Android).</em></p></div><ul data-testid=\"description:links\" class=\"DescriptionLinks_descriptionLinks__AHNFv\"><li><a data-testid=\"description:links:link\" href=\"/buying-guides/headphones-buying-guide\">Headphones Buying Guide</a></li></ul></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"P