details>','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/238135932?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','BOSE'),(117,'Marshall Minor III True Wireless Bluetooth In-Ear Headphones with Mic/Remote, Black','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined ProductAccordion_accordionWithKeyFeatures__zS4LS\" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Yes - 5.2</dd><dt>Noise Reduction or Cancelling<!-- -->:</dt><dd>No Noise Cancellation</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>44g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>True Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89731902</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Marshall amplifiers are iconic; a British brand that epitomises powerful, high-quality sound and the spirit of rock\'n\'roll. Their range of audio products are designed with the same attention to audio excellence, and brings the cool prestige of this classic company into the home.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Minor III</strong></p>\n\n<p>Experience Marshall signature sound with the freedom of totally wire-free listening with these discreet ear-buds. Enjoy up to 25 hours of power on-the-go with the included Marshall logo-emblazoned charging case.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Truly wireless listening</strong><br>\nWith two independent ear-buds fitting comfortably and securely in your ears, not a single wire gets in your way. Feel the inspiring freedom of truly wire-free listening, with a super-stable Bluetooth 5.2 connection.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Marshall sound</strong><br>\n12mm custom-tuned drivers deliver a loud and crisp sound, so you can be motivated by Marshall audio as you go about your day.</p>\n\n<p><strong>25 hours of power</strong><br>\nThe ear-buds last for up to 5 hours off a single charge, with the capacity for 20 hours stored in the charging case. Easily charge the case wirelessly (with a compatible wireless charging pad, sold separately), or via USB-C cable.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Intuitive control</strong><br>\nTouch-sensitivity on each ear-bud means easy control of music and phone calls. And when you remove and re-insert them, the tunes stop and start automatically, so you don\'t miss a beat, and save on battery power.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Iconic Marshall design</strong><br>\nThe textured black vinyl and familiar script logo highlight the heritage of a brand proudly boasting over fifty years of loud. </p>\n\n\n<p><em>These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p></div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-contain