\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89721315</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Enjoy super Sony sound as you go about your day with these wireless ear-buds. They’ll keep you in marvellous-sounding music for up to 25 hours of battery power, and when the juice is running a little low or you’re in a rush to get going, recharging for just ten minutes will keep ‘em going for up to another hour.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Enhanced Sony sonics</strong><br>\nThanks to clever Sony tech, you can be sure of great quality audio. Even when you’re listening to compressed music files, the brand’s Digital Sound Enhancement (DSEE) process brings the track closer to its original recording quality. Meaning a treat for the ears every time.</p>\n\n<p><strong>App happy</strong><br>\nPersonalise the sound experience too. Just choose from a list of audio presets to suit the genre of music you’re into that day, using the Sony Headphones Connect app. So whether you’re into banging metal or pounding electro, or prefer uplifting operatics and lush classical, the sound will always be optimised. And when you’re tapped by the perfectionist bug, you can use the equaliser in the app to create your very own custom presets. Nifty.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Worry-free water-resistance</strong><br>\nWhen you forget to check the forecast and get caught in a shower, the WI-C100 are IPX4 rated to protect against rain. Or even sweat if you’re using them to motivate your exercise.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Clear calls &amp; hands-free help</strong><br>\nHands-free calls are a breeze with a built-in mic. You’ll hear and be heard clearly when catching up on the goss. Plus, you can activate your smartphone’s voice assistant, so you only have to ask if you need hands-free help with directions, sending a message, …or inspiration for that next classic disco tune.</p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\