wn Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Yes - 5.0</dd><dt>Noise Reduction or Cancelling<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Noise Cancellation</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>307g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89710106</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Hear what your music <i>really</i> sounds like. If you’ve looked into acclaimed noise cancelling headphones, you’re probably aware of the PX7 from Bowers &amp; Wilkins. This S2 version sees them receive a raft of tweaks and upgrades for an even more exceptional listening experience. The speaker drivers have been revised and re-positioned for even better focus and distortion reduction, hybrid noise cancellation has been enhanced with a new algorithm, and their design has been revamped for even better comfort and sound isolation. Shut out the distractions of the world and hear your favourite music as the artist intended.</p>\n<p><strong>Premium Bowers &amp; Wilkins audio</strong><br>\nCustom-designed 40mm drive units are carefully angled inside each earcup for a truly focused listen. Bringing you closer to the original recording, the sound is detailed, natural and immersive. Combined with a 24-bit-capable wireless platform you get a truly immersive experience, allowing you to hear more of what the artist wants you to hear. Bluetooth supports aptX HD to ensure the best possible wireless connection. </p>\n<p><strong>Cancel outside noise, let the music shine</strong><br>\nThe PX7 S2 use a total of six microphones for outstanding noise cancellation that shuts out unwanted intrusions, but crucially, without harming your music’s dynamics and energy. As an added bonus, they also provide crystal-clear quality for calls from your smartphone too, even in noisy environments.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Music app</strong><br>\nEasily customise settings, or launch your phone’s voice assistant, with the Bowers &amp; Wilkins Music app on your smart device (available on iOS and Android).</p>\n\n<p><strong>More than all-day battery life</strong><br>\nThe PX7 S2 will keep you immersed in premium Bowers &amp; Wilkins sound quality for up to 30 hours off a single charge. And if you’re low on power, just fifteen minutes of charging gives you up to seven hours of listening.</p>\n<p><strong>Premium design, perfect fit</strong><br>\nThey’ve been crafted for comfortable, extended listening, with luxurious memory foam earpads that encapsulate and cushion the ears, and they’re finished in fine style with an elegant fabric-encased headband.</p>\n\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-tes