icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>YES</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>240g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89710522</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>The HD 450BT headphones give you superior Sennheiser sound with deep, dynamic bass, and noise cancellation. Sturdy and compact, with foldable design, touch controls let you control playback, take calls, and access your smart phone’s voice assistant.</p>\n<p><strong>Noise cancelling</strong><br>\nWith active noise cancellation and closed-back design, external noise is counteracted so you can enjoy your music without distraction.</p>\n<p><strong>Touch control</strong><br>\nIntuitive touch controls on the ear-cup let you control your music and phone calls. Access the voice assistant on your device with a dedicated button.</p>\n<p><strong>Foldable &amp; durable</strong><br>\nWith compact and durable design, the HD 450BT are foldable for easy storage and transport.</p>\n<p><strong>Wireless connection</strong><br>\nBluetooth, supported by AAC and aptX Low Latency codecs, assures a high quality, stable connection. And a full charge will keep them going for up to 30 hours of noise-cancelled music.</p>\n<p><st