gle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89730419</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Power through a punishing workout propelled by motivating music, or enjoy a subtle accompanying soundtrack to the weekend jog.  The Go Air Sport from JLab Audio are mighty and fun. They combine great sound with the freedom of true wireless listening, feature simple touch controls, and with Dual Connect, each earbud can be used independently. Take calls with ease, and they last for up to 32 hours with the included charging case. Auto-connect to your Bluetooth device to add music to your walk, run, HIIT session …whatever exercise floats your boat.</p>\n \n <p><strong>True wireless freedom</strong><br>\n With two independent earbuds fitting comfortably and securely in your ears, not a single wire gets in your way. Connect wirelessly with your smart device via a high-quality, stable Bluetooth connection.</p>\n \n <p><strong>JLab Audio sound</strong><br>\n Enjoy rich and crisp JLab Audio quality sound with 6mm drivers. And, with just a few taps on their touch sensors, you can tune to your preference with three EQ settings; Signature, Balanced, and Bass Boost, all without an app.</p>\n \n<p><strong>Dual connect</strong><br>\n The Go Air Sport connect automatically to your device once paired, and you’ll get a seamless connection, whether you’re using the earbuds independently or together. And you can take phone calls with ease with the built-in mic in either earbud.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Secure sport fit</strong><br>\nIP55 moisture-resistance holds up against sweat, rain and dirt, so you can hit the running trails, the gym …however you prefer to exercise. Their ergonomic earhooks fit even the smallest ears and ensure they stay securely and comfortably in place. Find the right size of gel ear-tips from the variety included, get a secure fit, and GO!</p>\n \n <p><strong>32 hour battery life</strong><br>\n They last for up to 8 hours off a single charge, with the power for an additional 24 hours in the included pocket-sized charging carry case. Recharge the case easily with the integrated charging cable.</p>\n \n <p><em>These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><dl data-testid=\"product:specification:list\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationList__HByhL\"><div class=