><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Yes - 5.2</dd><dt>Noise Reduction or Cancelling<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Active Noise Cancellation</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>46.2g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>True Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->85900220</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Samsung\'s Galaxy Buds 2 bring you rich bass and clear highs with a sleek 2-way dynamic speaker system. These true wireless earphones have a 3-mic system that ensures you can always hear your calls. Ambient Mode lets you know what\'s going on around you, while Active Noise Cancelling lets you focus on the music. They keep going for up to 20 hours with the included charging case, and offer seamless switching across Samsung devices*. And a snug, customisable fit keeps them comfortable all day long.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Immersive sound</strong><br>\nA 2-way dynamic speaker system with both a tweeter and a woofer produces powerful sound, with bold bass and clear highs, to ensure whatever you listen to sounds good.  Machine-based learning cancels out intrusive background noise like traffic or other sounds of the city, and a 3-way mic system ensures the voice is crystal clear when on a call.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tune in or tune out</strong><br>\nTwo mics detect the ambient noise around you and then technology takes over to minimise distraction. Immerse yourself in your favourite music and podcasts with Active Noise Cancelling, or, if you want to hear more of what\'s going on around you, Ambient Sound has three modes to suit you, so you can let the sound in without taking out your earbuds. Super low latency means you\'ll hear things exactly when they happen.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Power though playlists and podcasts</strong><br>\nStay tuned into your favourite songs, podcasts and videos for up to 20 hours** (the ear-buds will last for up to 5 hours, with the power for an additional 15 hours stored in the case). With seamless switching across Samsung devices*, you can move from a playlist on your phone to a video on your tablet, and the sound will swap seamlessly. With a Galaxy Watch 4 series (sold separately) you can control settings and check battery levels on your wrist. And if you misplace your Galaxy Buds 2, just use the helpful SmartThings Find app for assistance.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Small design, mighty sound</strong><br>\nWith three different sizes of soft silicone tips in the box, the fit is snug, comfortable and enhances Noise Cancellation. </p>\n\n\n<p>*Auto switching support is only available on Samsung phones and tablets using the Galaxy Wearable app, running One UI 3.1 or above, and must be signed in to the same Samsung account to use this feature.</p>\n\n<p>**Hours uninterrupted play time, plus extra hours when charged with the case. Battery life is based on usage of music or calls with Bluetooth and ANC turned on, and Always-on Mic turned off. </p>\n\n </div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.s