u get high-quality audio that’s just as impressive as what you’d hear from more expensive headphones.</p> \n\n<p>These EarPods work with compatible iPhone, iPad, Mac and iPod models.</p>\n\n\n\n\n <p><strong>Please note:</strong>The remote and mic are supported by all models of iPod, iPhone and iPad (not all models support volume up/down functions). Audio is supported by all iPod models.</p>  <p><strong>Volume control compatible with:</strong><br> iPhone 3GS and later<br> All iPad &amp; iPad mini models<br> iPod touch 2nd generation and later (Requires software version 2.2 or later) <br> iPod nano 4th generation and later (Requires software version 1.0.3 or later)<br> iPod classic 120GB (2008) or 160GB (2009) (Requires software version 2.0.1 or later) <br> iPod shuffle 4th generation</p></div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron