is.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/231827805?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','APPLE'),(127,'JBL Wave Flex True Wireless Bluetooth In-Ear Headphones with Mic/Remote, Black','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89723305</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Bring your sound everywhere. With bass you can feel, up to 32 total hours of battery life, and a secure, comfortable stick-open design, the splash and dust resistant JBL Wave Flex are designed for your daily entertainment. Whether you\'re roaming city streets or relaxing on the beach, your hands-free stereo calls will always be crystal clear, while Smart Ambient technology keeps you aware of your surroundings. And when you need an extra boost, you can speed-charge two additional hours of power in just 10 mins.</p>\n\n<p><b>True wireless freedom</b><br>\nWith two independent ear-buds fitting comfortably and securely in your ears, not a single wire gets in your way. Seamlessly connect the JBL Wave Flex to your smart device and enjoy excellent quality audio with a super stable Bluetooth connection.</p>\n	\n<p><b>JBL Deep Bass Sound</b><br>\nGet the most from your mixes with high-quality audio from secure, reliable earbuds with 12mm drivers featuring JBL Deep Bass Sound.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Hands-free calls with VoiceAware</b><br>\nEasily make hands-free stereo calls on the go. And with VoiceAware, you can choose how much of your own voice to hear by controlling the amount of mic input routed back into your earbuds.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Water and dust resistant</b><br>\nTheir IP54 water- and dust- resistance rating means you don’t have to worry, or be deterred by bad weather.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Up to 32 hours of playback</b><br>\nFrom a single charge, the ear-buds last for up to eight hours on their own, with the power for a further 24 hours stored in the case. And when you need a boost, just speed-charge for 10 minutes and get an extra 2 hours of battery life.</p>\n\n<p><em> These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p>	\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"butt