gn keeps them comfortable, even over the longer listen.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Consistently clear, crisp calls</strong><br>\nThanks to the three microphones on the Galaxy Buds FE, you are always clearly audible during phone calls. Main Mic, Sub Mic and Inner Mic all work together to convey your voice to the listener as best as possible.</p>\n\n<p><b>Battery life beauty</b><br>\nWith up to 30 hours of battery life (21 with noise cancelling enabled) with the included charging carry case, you can keep your music motivating you through the busiest and longest of days …and on into the night!</p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><dl data-testid=\"product:specification: