\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89712216</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>B&amp;O’s H95 wireless headphones offer exceptional comfort, the premium sound of Bang &amp; Olufsen, and exceptional Noise Cancellation. Celebrating 95 years of the brand’s audio heritage, they’re ideal headphones for travellers, providing you with a pure focus on your music, or even peaceful silence, in any environment. Tuned by the company’s acoustic engineers, they deliver outstanding sound performance and a seamless Bluetooth 5.1 wireless connection. Crafted from premium materials, they provide long lasting comfort. Immerse yourself in pure, luxurious sound.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Noise cancelling that adapts</strong><br>\nActive Noise Cancellation automatically adjusts according to the environment. So you’re able to shut out the world and fully immerse yourself in your music. Completely focus on a phone call, or just envelop yourself in silence.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Signature B&amp;O sound</strong><br>\nWith two customised 40mm titanium drivers and its digital signal processing engine, B&amp;O’s acoustic engineers ensure the supreme sound of Bang &amp; Olufsen is delivered wirelessly. With increased low frequency response for deep, lush bass, mids are also richly detailed, and highs are superbly delicate and precise.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Intuitive control</strong><br>\nElegant and intuitive user controls allow quick toggling between noise cancelling, transparency modes (when you need to let some external sound in), and other functions.</p> \n\n<p><strong>Clear calls</strong><br>\nFour built-in microphones make all your calls crystal clear, and the H95 support voice assistant technology, so you can interact by speaking with your smart phone still in your pocket, thanks to their dedicated button.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Luxurious design</strong><br>\nWith oval earcups and soft lambskin ear cushions with memory foam, the premium materials of the H95 ensure they stay comfortable over long listening periods. Every element is designed to balance looks with performance, from precision aluminium dials to their detachable ear cushions. With folding design, they’re safely stored and protected in the plushly-lined aluminium carry case.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Long-lasting</strong><br>\nThe H95 last for up to 38 hours of listening with noise cancelling turned on, so you can listen in comfort day and night.</p></div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgr