ined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89710504</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Acclaimed for a supreme balance of audio excellence, premium design and luxurious comfort, Sennheiser’s Momentum range continues to redefine the standard for sophisticated listening. This fourth generation unites the best of a superior Sennheiser sound experience, exceptional comfort, and smart convenience.</p><p>\n</p><p><strong>Superior Sennheiser sound</strong><br>\nThey’re powered by the brand’s audiophile-inspired 42mm transducer system for exceptional high-fidelity. You can listen your way with built-in presets, sound modes, and the Sound Personalisation feature which tailors it specifically to your own ear. All accessible via the Sennheiser Smart Control app. Support for SBC, AAC, and aptX Adaptive codecs ensures the highest quality connection option is automatically selected for your device, making wireless as good as a wired connection. </p>\n<p><strong>Adaptive Noise Cancellation</strong><br>\nAdvanced noise cancellation  (ANC) automatically adapts to your surroundings, keeping out the distractions of the outside world, so you can fully focus on the music. And when you do need to be aware of what’s happening around you, just engage Transparency Mode and stay safely aware without needing to remove the headphones.</p>\n<p><strong>Crystal clear calls</strong><br>\nFour digital beam-forming microphones ensure high quality voice pick-up and automatic wind noise suppression for optimised call quality and easy voice assistant access.</p>\n<p><strong>Exceptional comfort, premium design</strong><br>\nTheir lightweight design includes padded headband and deep cushioned ear-pads to ensure a premium level of comfort, even over the longer listen. And they fold flat for easy storage and transport in the included soft fabric and protective hard-shell case.</p>\n<p><strong>Seamless control</strong><br>\nIntuitive touch control gives you control of music, ANC, calls and voice assistant acess. Auto On/Off means they switch on just by picking them up, and power down to save energy after 15 minutes not in use. When you take them off, Smart Pause auto-stops the current track and resumes when you put them back on again.</p>\n<p><strong>Exceptional battery life</strong><br>\nThe Momentum 4 Wireless last for up to a huge 60 hours of playtime off a single charge, and when you eventually do get low on power, support for fast-charging gets you back up and running in no time.</p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.sv