240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89733707</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Shokz bring their open-ear concept to the true wireless market with OpenFit. An alternative to in-ear buds (which can sometimes feel a little invasive), they let you enjoy easy all-day comfort and hear your personal soundtrack, while still staying fully aware of the environment you’re in. Ultra-lightweight, open-ear construction means you receive <em>both</em> your own audio, <em>and</em> the sound around you, with crystal-clear clarity. The brand’s DirectPitch tech produces rich, full-frequency audio so you can immerse yourself in your preferred soundtracks, podcasts, and audiobooks, while flexible ear-hook design combines comfort with reliable stability. Now you can really hear every moment.</p>\n<p><b>Open-ear comfort</b><br>\nEnjoy exceptional comfort thanks to the open-ear design of OpenFit, which allows for a secure, but non-invasive fit. In fact, with each bud weighing only 8.3g, you\'ll hardly notice they\'re there.</p>\n<p><b>High-quality audio</b><br>\n18 × 11mm customised speaker drivers ensure an excellent acoustic experience. Exclusive technologies like DirectPitch and OpenBass replicate live concert-like listening.</p>\n<p><b>Safe situational awareness</b><br>\nWith the brand’s signature open-ear design, the OpenFit wireless headphones allow you to hear the ambient sounds around you, making it ideal and safe for use outdoors as well as in …at home ….in the office …in the great outdoors …wherever!</p>\n<p><b>Stable and secure</b><br>\nErgonomic ear hooks and Bluetooth 5.2 ensure OpenFit stay in place and maintain a stable and smooth audio connection, even when you’re powering through your most intense training.</p>\n<p><b>Long battery life</b><br>\nPower your whole day …and beyond… with up to 28 hours of battery life using the included charging case. And, if you’re low on power, just five minutes of Quick Charge gives you an hour of listening.</p></div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><dl data-testid=\"product:specification:list\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationList__HByhL\"><div class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListItem__2KCOH\"><dd data-testid=\"product:specification:list:label\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabel__oJ2G6\"><span class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabelName__vvnKU\">Accessories Included</span><