uld you want?</p>\n\n<p><b>Razer TriForce drivers</b><br>\nTo be clear, these sound great. Unlike traditional single-range designs, Razer designed each driver to be able to focus on bass, midrange and treble separately. We won\'t get too techy with it - just know they\'ll deliver richer trebles, punchier mids and powerful bass.</p>\n\n<p><b>Razer HyperClear mic</b><br>\nWhether you’re chatting with teammates or trash-talking the enemy, Razer\'s HyperClear Mic makes sure you\'re heard loud and clear. It\'ll amplify your voice and dampen any other sound that\'s around you. Feel free to adjust things too - Razer\'s Synapse software gives you access to mic settings that can be customized to enhance your sound.</p>\n\n<p><b>Memory foam ear cushions</b><br>\nRazer knows things can intense whatever game you\'re playing. That\'s why the foam surrounding the headset minimizes sweat and heat build-up. So enjoy the game distraction-free.</p>\n\n<p><b>Dedicated mobile mic</b><br>\nHidden in this headset is a second mic that\'s super handy when you need to talk while commuting, whether it’s for mobile gaming or answering work calls.</p>\n\n<p><b>EQ toggle and Xbox paring</b><br>\nHold down the button on the right ear cup to pair your headset easily. Press it twice to cycle through 4 EQ settings that enhance in-game audio like enemy footsteps and low-frequency sounds.</p>\n\n\n\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\