ss=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>The 3rd Gen AirPods have been re-designed and enhanced to heighten the music listening experience. They support immersive Spatial Audio content so you\'re at the heart of a 3D sound-scape for your music and shows. Adaptive EQ fine-tunes the sound for optimum delivery, they\'re sweat and water-resistant, and they last for up to 6 hours off a single charge, or up to 30 hours with the included Lightning and wireless compatible charging case.</p>\n<p><strong>Re-designed</strong><br>\nWith a lightweight and contoured design, they sit at just the right angle for comfort, as well as music delivery. The stem is shorter than the previous generation, and includes a force sensor for easy control of both your music and calls.</p>\n<p><strong>Spatial audio</strong><br>\nSupporting spatial audio from compatible sources, sound is placed all around you for a three-dimensional, immersive listen. And with dynamic head tracking tech, it sounds like you\'re at the centre of what you\'re listening to.</p>\n<p><strong>Adaptive EQ</strong><br>\nWith Adaptive EQ, music is automatically tuned to suit your ear, with inward-facing microphones that detect what you\'re hearing and adjust frequencies to deliver every detail.</p>\n\n<p><strong>H1 chip </strong><br>\nApple\'s H1 chip ensures your AirPods will have better connectivity, increased battery life and speedier pairing times. It also provides lower gaming latency and voice-enabled Siri access.</p> \n\n<p><strong>Sweat and water-resistant</strong><br>\nBoth the AirPods and the charging case are IPX4 water-resistant, so you can use them with confidence in all weathers, or when exercising hard at the gym.</p>\n<p><strong>Longer battery life</strong><br>\nThey last for up to six hours of listening time (four hours of talk time), with a skin-detecting sensor to turn them on and off automatically, preserving energy when not in use. And when you\'re short on time, a quick 5 minute charge gives you around an hour of power. The included Lightning charging case carries enough charge for up to 30 hours of battery life, and can be recharged using the included Lightning to USB-C cable.</p>\n<p><strong>Use your way</strong><br>\nThey\'re ready to go right out of the case, and can automatically switch between your Apple devices. You can also get Siri to read your notifications through the AirPods, so you\'re always in the know.</p>\n<p>Full functionality requires the latest OS version on your Apple device.</p>\n\n<p>These AirPods work with compatible iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple Watch, Apple TV and iPod models.</p></div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-ac