romiseactive=\"true\"></jl-reviews></div></div></details>','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/109467540?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','APPLE'),(140,'Google Pixel Buds A-Series True Wireless Bluetooth In-Ear Headphones, Carbon','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->85900107</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Google\'s Pixel Buds A-Series are helpful ear-buds, designed for the way that you move. Enjoy full, crisp audio for songs, videos and calls. These true wireless ear-buds are made to look great and stay firmly in place, even when you\'re working out. Connected to a compatible Android device, Google gives you answers and updates when you need them, you just have to ask.* And with the included charging case, you can keep listening for up to 24 hours.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Premium adaptive sound and clear calls</strong><br>\nThese true wireless ear-buds deliver rich, high-quality audio. Custom-designed speaker drivers give you powerful bass and crisp highs. Beam-forming mics focus on your voice, so the person that you\'re talking to on a call hears you loud and clear. And as you move between noisy and quiet places, Adaptive Sound adjusts the volume on your headphones to fit your surroundings.** </p>\n\n<p><strong>Made to stay in while you work out</strong><br>\nThey have a comfortable, stylish fit that can keep up with you during workouts. With a flush-to-ear design, three ear tip sizes and a stabiliser arc, the ear-buds stay in place and create a gentle seal for amazing sound.</p> \n\n<p><strong>Tap to control</strong><br>\nTouch controls let you answer calls, play, pause and skip between tracks easily. </p>\n\n<p><strong>Sweat and water resistant</strong><br>\nThe wireless earbuds aren\'t afraid of a little water, so rainy days and sweaty workouts are no problem. The ear-buds have a rating of IPX4 (not the charging case).</p>\n\n<p><strong>Hands-free help</strong><br>\nWhen you need directions, help with translations or notifications read to you, just ask Google.*</p>\n\n<p><strong>Long lasting battery</strong><br>\nThese wireless ear-buds provide what you need to enjoy the music that you love without interruption. You can get up to 5 hours of listening time, or 2.5 hours of talk time, on a single charge, or listen for up to 24 hours with the included charging case.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Connect and get going</strong><br>\nPair your ear-buds with any Android device in just one tap (Fast Pair requires Location setting enabled). And easily connect to iOS or any other Bluetooth 4.0+ device. If you should misplace them, hear them ring with Find My Device if they\'re nearby, or see their last known location on a map.*** </p><br>\n<p>*Google Assistant requires a Google Assistant-enabled Android 6.0 device, Google Account and an Internet connection. Data rates may apply. For available languages and minimum requirements go to g.co/pixelbuds/help.</p>\n\n<p>**Adaptive Sound requires an Android 6.0 or newer device to enable the feature.</p>\n\n<p>***Requires Google Pixel B