2px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Yes - 5.1</dd><dt>Noise Reduction or Cancelling<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Noise Cancellation</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>26g</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89733703</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Shokz’ OpenRun are next-level bone conduction sport Headphones. Built for running performance, they’re lightweight, comfortable, IP67 waterproof (not suitable for swimming), and last for up to eight hours off one charge. They also have a quick-charge feature so 10-minutes gives you 1.5 hours of listening time so you can get on-the-go fast! This Mini version is designed for max comfort for the smaller head. </p>\n\n<p><strong>Mini size, max comfort</strong> <br>\nOpenRun Mini Bluetooth headphones don\'t go in or over your ears, ensuring your ears are always dry and cool even when running on hot humid days. Feather-light and with a 21mm smaller headband than the standard size, the OpenRun Mini fits those with smaller heads snugly without weighing down the ears.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Bud-free comfort</strong><br>\nUnlike traditional wireless earphones, bone conduction headphones sit in front of your ears leaving them open, they do not cause your ears to become hot. With a lightweight design of only 26g, you will barely notice them while running or exercising even on the hottest days.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Open-ear safety</strong><br>\nThe OpenRun sports headphones feature an open-ear design to provide the safest way to enjoy music or podcasts while running, cycling, sprinting, or hiking, without blocking your surroundings. This will effectively prevent a number of risky situations.</p>\n\n<p><strong>IP67 waterproof</strong><br>\nAs a pioneer of bone conduction technology, we work on safe sport and are the only sports headphones brand recommended by England Athletics. IP67 waterproof wireless headphones fully consider the outdoor environment during exercise, perfect for intense workouts. (Not suitable for swimming)</p>\n\n<p><strong>8 hour battery life</strong><br>\nThe quick charge feature together with long endurance of Bluetooth v5.1 provides an uninterrupted musical journey even during full Marathons, and, with its Dual noise-cancelling mics, further enhance the listening experience by providing crystal clear sound.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Superb sound quality </strong><br>\nOpenRun Bluetooth headphones offer cutting-edge technology to ensure remarkable sound quality and come with a two-year warranty.</p>\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1q