\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89733706</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>OpenSwim takes open-ear listening to new depths. IP68 waterproof design withstands total submersion in up to 2 metres of water. With up to 8-hours powerful battery life and 4GB of storage (that’s around 1200 songs), you can enjoy extraordinary underwater sound quality. It’s a superior choice for swimming, accompanying your waterborne exercise with an aquatic soundtrack.</p>\n<p><b>Open-ear comfort</b><br>\nUnlike in-ear headphones, OpenSwim are equipped with an open-ear design powered by bone conduction technology, ensuring bud-free and comfortable listening all day …in or out of the water.</p>\n\n<p><b>IP68 waterproof</b><br>\nWith this waterproof rating, they’ll withstand total submersion in up to 2 metres of water. Fully waterproof and submersible, you can swim, or even run, cycle, or train harder than ever before.</p>\n\n<p><b>Excellent underwater sound quality</b><br>\nBoosted by 7th generation bone conduction technology, the OpenSwim give you clear and consistent sound quality throughout all your swimming strokes and turns.</p>\n\n<p><b>Versatile and secure</b><br>\nOpenFit titanium design is equipped with wraparound flexibility for reliable stability. So they’re comfortably compatible with swim caps, goggles, and earplugs.</p>\n\n<p><b>4GB internal storage, 8 hour battery</b><br>\nWith 4GB of storage for MP3s, you can swim accompanied by around about 1200 tracks. Their powerful battery lasts for up to eight hours so you can keep swimming, and enjoy their great underwater sound quality.</p>\n<p>Shokz OpenSwim are not Bluetooth compatible</p></div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><dl data-tes