i-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-24px-outlined.e35fd2be.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5\" style=\"max-height:100%\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->70413807</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>With Soundform Bolt you’ll keep the music going with up to 28 hours for longer listening, and seamlessly connect and switch between devices with Bluetooth 5.2 technology. 6mm dynamic drivers deliver smooth, clear sound quality, and the light, ergonomic earbud design places the buds comfortably and snugly in the ears for longer listening pleasure. IPX4-rated materials enable use in rainy weather and sweaty workouts, while Mono Mode allows use of one earbud at a time to extend battery life and stay alert of your surroundings.</p>\n\n<p><b>Long-lasting charge</b><br>\nUp to 28 hours of battery life — 9 hours of playtime per charge for the earbuds, plus another 19 hours of battery in the charging case. Mono Mode allows use of one earbud at a time to extend battery life and stay alert of your surroundings.</p>\n\n<p><b>Quick pairing</b><br>\nThe reliable Bluetooth 5.2 chipset offers easy connection and pairing from 10 metres. All you need to worry about is what to play first!</p>\n\n<p><b>Great audio every day</b><br>\nThe 6mm dynamic drivers provide consistently smooth, crisp audio that’s perfect for everyday listening, so you can fully appreciate your favourite playlists.</p>\n\n<p><b>Comfortable fit</b><br>\nThese light, ergonomic earbuds sit comfortably and snugly in the ears. It’s easy to enjoy calls and playlists for hours.</p>\n\n<p><b>Control with a tap</b><br>\nWire-free, button-free touch controls in both earbuds let you tap to adjust volume, skip tracks, pick up and end calls.</p>\n\n<p><b>Water resistance? No sweat</b><br>\nDon’t let light rain or a challenging workout get in the way of being connected. Built with IPX4 water and sweat resistance, these wireless earbuds help move you through everyday activities worry-free.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>These True Wireless headphones are compatible with all smart devices with Bluetooth, including from Apple, Samsung and Google, and other Android smart phone brands.</em></p></div></div></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj accordion_c-accordion--medium-size__cRL0j\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_ accordion_c-accordion__label--medium-size__yrX5v\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF accordion_c-accordion__chevron--medium-size__5dItE\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-24px-outlined.e35fd2be.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><dl data-testid=\"product:specification:list\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationList__HByhL\"><div class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListItem__2KCOH\"><dd data-testid=\"product:specification:list:label\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabel__oJ2G6\"><span class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabelName__vvnKU\">Accessories Included</span><div data-testid=\"product:specification:list:tooltip\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabelToolTip__m6seg\"><div class=\"ProductSpecification_tooltipWrapper__E9uN8\"></div></div></dd><dt data-test