r\'s packed the Kraken V3 Pro with haptic feedback then. With the ability to feel what you hear, gaming has never felt this intense or real.</p>\n\n<p><b>Feedback that feels real</b><br>\nCutting-edge haptic drivers in each earcup pick up on audio cues and convert them into realistic vibrations that vary in position, duration, and intensity, providing touch-sensory feedback for in-game sounds.</p>\n\n<p><b>Razer TriForce drivers</b><br>\nTo be clear, these sound great. Unlike traditional single-range designs, Razer designed each driver to be able to focus on bass, midrange and treble separately. We won\'t get too techy with it - just know they\'ll deliver richer trebles, punchier mids and powerful bass.</p>\n\n<p><b>THX spatial audio</b><br>\nThe headset also comes armed with advanced 7.1 surround sound that optimizes your game’s sound design for realistic positional audio. Experience true-to-life acoustics and hear everything as if you were right in the middle of it all.\n\n</p><p><b>Razer HyperClear mic</b><br>\nWhether you’re chatting with teammates or trash-talking the enemy, Razer\'s HyperClear Mic makes sure you\'re heard loud and clear. It\'ll amplify your voice and dampen any other sound that\'s around you. Feel free to adjust things too - Razer\'s Synapse software gives you access to mic settings that can be customized to enhance your sound.</p>\n\n<p><b>Memory foam ear cushions</b><br>\nRazer knows things can intense whatever game you\'re playing. That\'s why the foam surrounding the headset minimizes sweat and heat build-up. So enjoy the game distraction-free.</p>\n\n<p><b>RGB that\'s off the charts</b><br>\nBask in the Kraken\'s glory as you choose from over 16.8 million colours and countless lighting effects, all while it reacts dynamically with over 150 Chroma-integrated games.</p>\n\n<p><b>Compatibility</b><br>\n<b> - PC (wireless, wired)<br>\n<b> - PlayStation (wireless, wired)<br>\n<b> - Nintendo Switch (wireless in docked mode, wired)<br>\n<b> - Mobile Devices (wired)</b></b></b></b></p>\nXbox (wired)</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><dl data-testid=\"product:specification:list\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationList__HByhL\"><div class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListItem__2KCOH\"><dd data-testid=\"product:specification:list:label\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabel__oJ2G6\"><span class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabelName__vvnKU\">Brand</span><div data-testid=\"product:specification:list:tooltip\" class=\"ProductSpecification_productSpecificationListLabelToolTip__m6seg\"><div class=\"ProductSpecification_tooltipWrapper__E9uN8\