ace your headphones to get the latest, greatest features. That is good for your budget and good for the planet. </p><p>Skullcandy Crusher is the original, one-and-only immersive sensory bass experience. Turn the adjustment wheel down for more mellow bass or turn it up to really rattle your bones. Crusher ANC 2 also features voice-controlled Crusher Bass. </p><p>Crusher ANC 2 is equipped with premium 4-mic active noise cancelling that detects and cancels noise in the full range of sounds you can hear. Our advanced ANC is adjustable, too — so you can set your own custom level using a slider in the Skull-iQ App. </p><p>Headphone Features</p><ul><li>Foam ear pieces. </li><li>1m cord length. </li><li>Detachable cable. </li><li>Connection: wireless and wired. </li><li>Bluetooth enabled for a wireless connection to your devices . </li><li>Connects to devices via Bluetooth 5.0. </li><li>With a USB-C connection. </li><li>3.5mm jack . </li><li>40mm driver. </li><li>On ear controls. </li><li>Adjustable headband. </li><li>Foldable. </li><li>Active noise cancellation. </li><li>10m range. </li><li>Carry case. </li><li>Bass control. </li><li>Compatible with universal smartphones. </li><li>Batteries required 1 x lithium battery (included) . </li><li>Rechargeable battery. </li><li>50 hour battery life. </li><li>150 minute charging time. </li><li>Fast charge to boost battery life. </li><li>In the box: Headphone, Carry Case, Charging and Audio Cable. </li></ul><p>General Information</p><ul><li>Model number: S6CAW-R740. </li><li>Manufacturer\'s 1 year guarantee. </li><li>EAN: 810045688817. </li><li>Warning - Not suitable for children under the age of 3 years due to small parts and entanglement hazard. </li></ul>','https://media.4rgos.it/i/Argos/3201947_R_Z001A?w=1000&h=1000&qlt=70&fmt=webp','SKULLCANDY'),(176,'Sony WH-CH520 On-Ear Wireless Bluetooth Headphones - Black','<p>Introducing the WH-CH520 Wireless Bluetooth Headphones, for a high-quality listening experience for music and call