</span></div></div></div></div><span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div class=\"\"><jl-reviews data-testid=\"product:reviews\" productid=\"110194491\" producturl=\"/sony-wh-ch720-noise-cancelling-bluetooth-wireless-on-ear-headphones-with-mic-remote/p110194491\" apikey=\"AIzaSyDrfSLzq-WxgyLPSKu53oW7y4TJo7bQdpY\" clientid=\"standard-pdp-ui\" modalrootid=\"page-root\" accordion=\"true\" displaytitle=\"false\" experiments=\"\" isbrandpromiseactive=\"true\"></jl-reviews></div></div></details>','https://johnlewis.scene7.com/is/image/JohnLewis/110163004?$rsp-pdp-port-640-82$','SONY'),(199,'Belkin SoundForm Mini Kids Wireless On-Ear Headphones -Black','<p>Premium quality SoundForm headphones, reimagined for kids with distance learning, travel, and streaming online content in mind. These Mini Wireless On-Ear Headphones are kid friendly in every way, from their volume cap of 85 dB, to their easy-to-use controls and durable oops-proof design. With up to 30 hours of non-stop playtime, the headphones will last all through the school week, and are tested to work with today\'s most popular learning devices and apps. </p><p>Long life battery. Up to 30 hours of playtime. That\'s only one charge per week. </p><p>Backpeak function. Thanks to the built-in microphone, children can talk to teachers and friends. </p><p>Volume cap. Decibel levels won\'t exceed 85 dB to protect children\'s ears from damage. </p><p>Headphone Features</p><ul><li>Detachable cable. </li><li>Connection: wireless and wired. </li><li>Bluetooth enabled for a wireless connection to your devices . </li><li>Connects to devices via Bluetooth. </li><li>With a 3.5mm jack connection. </li><li>On ear controls. </li><li>Adjustable headband. </li><li>10m range. </li><li>Water-resistant. </li><li>Compatible with universal smartphones. </li><li>Batteries required 1 x (included) . </li><li>Rechargeable battery. </li><li>30 hour battery life. </li><li>In the box: Mini Wireless On-Ear Headphones, Micro-USB cable, 3.5mm cable. </li></ul><p>General Information</p><ul><li>Model number: AUD002BTBK. </li><li>Manufacturer\'s 1 year guarantee. </li><li>EAN: 745883820504. </li></ul>','https://media.4rgos.it/i/Argos/9512836_R_Z001A?w=1000&h=1000&qlt=70&fmt=webp','BELKIN'),(200,'Belkin SoundForm Nano Kids In-Ear True Wireless Earbuds -Wht','<p>Kids 7 and up can enjoy all-day comfort with a sealed in-ear fit while being protected by an 85dB volume limiter. Ready for plenty of song and video plays. They\'re water and sweat resistant with an IPX5 rating. </p><p>A volume cap of 85dB protects kids\' ears while they listen, learn and play. </p><p>SoundForm Nano earbuds offer 5 hours of playtime and another 19 hours of charge in the case. </p><p>Compatible with all Bluetooth-enabled devices including smartphones, tablets, and laptops, and the 30 ft. /10m range keeps kids connected to their devices even if they move around while listening. </p><p>Headphone Features</p><ul><li>Silicon ear pieces. </li><li>Connection: true wireless. </li><li>Bluetooth enabled for a wireless connection to your devices . </li><li>Connects to devices via Wi-Fi. </li><li>6mm driver. </li><li>On ear controls. </li><li>10m range. </li><li>Carry case. </li><li>Water-resistant. </li><li>IPX5 water resistant. </li><li>Compatible with universal smartphones. </li><li>Batteries required 1 x Li-Ion battery (included) . </li><li>Rechargeable battery. </li><li>5 hour battery life. </li><li>120 minute charging time. </li><li>Fast charge to boost battery life. </li><li>Charging case included. </li><li>In the box: Earbuds, charging case, micro USB cable, 5 pairs silicon eartips and quick start guide. </li></ul><p>General Information</p><ul><li>Model number: PAC003BTWH. </li><li>Manufacturer\'s 2 year guarantee. </li><li>EAN: 745883841554. </li><li>Warning - Not suitable for children under the age of 3 years due to small parts and entanglement hazard. </li></ul>','https://media.4rgos.it/i/Argos/1879931_R_Z001A?w=1000&h=1000&qlt=70&fmt=webp','BELKIN'),(201,'Marshall Minor III Wireless Earbuds','<p>Minor III brings you Marshall signature sound without any extra clutter. These headphones do all the heavy lifting for you, so you can just grab your music and go. Enjoy the absolute freedom of listening without wires. Minor III comes with Bluetooth 5.2, ensuring that each earbud has a strong connection to your device. You don\'t want to be left stranded without music when you need it most, so Minor III packs 25 total hours of wireless playtime to keep you moving. Carry additional charges in your pocket with the compact portable charging case. </p><p>25 hours of wireless playtime. </p><p>Intuitive touch controls. </p><p>Custom-tuned drivers. </p><p>Headphone Features</p><ul><li>Plastics (PC/ABS), Electronical Components (Cables, PCBs, Magnets, Drivers), Li-ion batteries. Magnets, Silicone, Steel, Fabric mesh, Plastic tape ear pieces. </li><li>USB-C cord. </li><li>Connection: true wireless. </li><li>Bluetooth enabled for a wireless connection to your devices . </li><li>Connects to devices via Bluetooth. </li><li>Touch controls on side controls. </li><li>Passive noise cancellation. </li><li>Carry case. </li><li>Water-resistant. </li><li>IPX4 splashproof. </li><li>Compatible with iOS smartphones. </li><li>(included) . </li><li>Rechargeable battery. </li><li>25 hour battery life. </li><li>120 minute charging time. </li><li>Fast charge to boost battery life. </li><li>Charging case included. </li><li>In the box: Minor III true wireless headphones, Charging case, USB-C charging cable, Quick start guide and legal &amp; safety information. </li></ul><p>General Information</p><ul><li>Model number: 1