nt__v6BoV\"><div class=\"KeyFeatures_keyFeatures__QGm5K\"><h2>Key features</h2><dl><dt>Bluetooth Enabled<!-- -->:</dt><dd>YES</dd><dt>Power Supply<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Rechargable Battery</dd><dt>Weight<!-- -->:</dt><dd>0.85kg</dd><dt>Wired or Wireless<!-- -->:</dt><dd>Wireless</dd></dl></div><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89711114</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Beats’ Solo Wireless headphones have been upgraded and refined, delivering award-winning Beats sound quality with a massively improved 40 hour battery life. Class 1 Bluetooth technology gives wireless freedom, sleek and durable design emphasises comfort and coolness, while the headset has integrated controls for music playback and hands-free calls. Beats Solo³ are an awesome audio accessory for an emotionally-charged wireless listening experience and multiple all-day use.</p>\n<p><strong>Award-winning Audio</strong><br>\nBeats Solo³ headphones offer award-winning Beats audio quality, with fine-tuned acoustics that maximise clarity, breadth and balance. Comfort-cushion ear-cups buffer outside noise for a fully immersive music experience.</p>\n<p><strong>Boosted Battery</strong><br>\nWith a battery powered by the Apple W1 chip, you can stay unplugged for up to 40 hours of wireless listening, enough for multiple days of use without recharging. Easily keep track of the battery level with the illuminated LED gauge on the headset, and recharge via Micro-USB port. The Fast Fuel feature means that, when the battery is low, just 5 minutes of charging will give 3 hours of listening.</p>\n<p><strong>Convenient Control</strong><br>\nThe integrated on-ear control and microphone gives you easy command of track selection, volume level and hands-free phone calls, and is fully compatible with Siri.</p>\n<strong>Durable Design</strong><br>\nWith iconic Beats design, the Solo³ Wireless are built for durability and comfort. Ergonomically designed on-ear cushioned ear-cups optimise sound delivery and are adjustable for a fully customisable fit, to ensure all day comfort. For convenience they can be fully folded and stored in the carry case provided.<p></p></div><ul data-testid=\"description:links\" class=\"DescriptionLinks_descriptionLinks__AHNFv\"><li><a data-testid=\"description:links:link\" href=\"/buying-guides/headphones-buying-guide\">Headphones Buying Guide</a></li></ul></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/plus/plus-24px-outlined.606d8737.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Plus Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Plus Icon\"></div></div><div class=\"button_tertiary-content__9N1qT\"><span>Show more</span></div></button></div></div></details><details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj\" data-testid=\"accordion:specification\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product specification<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-l