ucing the Sony WH-1000XM5 - our industry-leading noise cancellation just took its biggest step up! With four microphones on each earcup, ambient sound is captured even more accurately to deliver unprecedented noise cancelling quality. Hi-Res Audio and Hi-Res Audio Wireless are supported, thanks to LDAC, transmitting approximately three times more data than conventional Bluetooth audio. These headphones promise industry-leading call quality. Pair with two devices at the same time. Features Fast Pair and Swift Pair. </p><p>The new Integrated Processor V1 unlocks the full potential of our HD Noise Cancelling Processor QN1 to deliver our biggest step forward in our (already) industry-leading noise cancellation technology. </p><p>Precision-engineered to deliver exceptional High-Resolution Audio quality. Our Precise Voice Pickup Technology with newly developed wind noise reduction will also ensure you can hear and be heard clearly when taking calls on these noise cancelling headphones. </p><p>Smart, intuitive, and intelligent. Adaptive Sound Control automatically adjusts the sound settings based on your environment and activity, and Speak-to-Chat automatically pauses the music when you want to have a conversation, without you having to remove the over ear headphones! </p><p>Headphone Features</p><ul><li>Gold plated L-shaped cord. </li><li>Detachable cable. </li><li>Connection: true wireless. </li><li>Bluetooth enabled for a wireless connection to your devices . </li><li>With a 3.5mm jack connection. </li><li>30mm driver. </li><li>Touch controls on side controls. </li><li>Adjustable headband. </li><li>Active noise cancellation. </li><li>10m range. </li><li>Carry case. </li><li>Bass control. </li><li>Compatible with universal smartphones. </li><li>Batteries required 2 x Li-Ion battery (included) . </li><li>30 hour battery life. </li><li>210 minute charging time. </li><li>Fast charge to boost battery life. </li><li>In the box: Carry Case, Connection Cable, USB Cable, Warranty Card &amp; Reference Guide. </li></ul><p>General Information</p><ul><li>Model number: WH1000XM5L. CE7. </li><li>Manufacturer\'s 1 year guarantee. </li><li>EAN: 4548736134294. </li><li>Warning - Not suitable for children under the age of 3 years due to small parts and entanglement hazard. </li><li>Caution – To prevent possible hearing damage, do not listen at high volume for long periods. </li></ul>','https://media.4rgos.it/i/Argos/2843492_R_Z001A?w=1000&h=1000&qlt=70&fmt=webp','SONY'),(239,'Samsung Galaxy Buds Plus Earbud Noise-Cancelling Bluetooth Earphones','Samsung Galaxy Buds Plus Earbud Noise-Cancelling Bluetooth Earphones - Black','https://www.backmarket.co.uk/cdn-cgi/image/format%3Dauto%2Cquality%3D75%2Cwidth%3D260/https://d2e6ccujb3mkqf.cloudfront.net/b6744a91-1a0c-4749-b87c-b783ecc571d1-1_267a90c6-a9ff-4855-9783-812103465607.jpg','SAMSUNG'),(240,'Bose QuietComfort QC45 SE Noise Cancelling Over-Ear Wireless Bluetooth Headphones with Mic/Remote, Black','<details class=\"accordion_c-accordion__9k_Yj undefined \" data-testid=\"accordion:description\" id=\"accordion-description\" open=\"\"><summary role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"accordion_c-accordion__label__5nJU_\">Product description<span class=\"accordion_c-accordion__chevron__DSgrF\"><img src=\"https://www.johnlewis.com/static/ui-assets/hashed/icons-jb/chevron-down/chevron-down-32px-outlined.8c7029b0.svg\" class=\"\" alt=\"Chevron Down Icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Chevron Down Icon\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion_c-accordion__content__v6BoV\"><div><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContainer___sKm5 ProductDescription_truncated__MXk73\" style=\"max-height: 240px;\" id=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:accordion:container\"><p data-testid=\"description:code\" class=\"ProductDescription_productCode__PVgM8\"><strong>Product code: <!-- -->89710304</strong></p><div class=\"ProductDescription_descriptionContent__N2Oh0\" data-testid=\"description:content\"><p>Bose\'s original noise-cancelling headphones are back in upgraded form, with even better levels of quiet, an Aware mode, supremely light materials for premium comfort, and proprietary acoustic technology for deep, clear audio. The Quietcomfort QC45 SE wireless headphones offer an ideal balance of quiet, comfort and sound.</p>\n\n<p>This SE special edition of Bose\'s Quietcomfort QC45 headphones includes a soft carry case.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Acoustic Noise Cancelling</strong><br>\nTiny microphones hidden in the earcups measure, compare and react to outside noise. External sound is cancelled with an opposite audio signal, meaning fewer distractions, and more focus on the music. Choose between Quiet Mode for full noise cancelling, or Aware Mode to let in some surrounding sound.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Aware Mode</strong><br>\nAware Mode keeps you safely aware of the outside world with microphones that pick up the sounds around you, playing them naturally through the headphones. An audio mix of your music and your environment leads to a feeling of not wearing headphones at all.</p>\n\n<p><strong>High fidelity music</strong><br>\nExclusive Bose technologies like TriPort acoustic architecture and Volume-optimised Active EQ deliver high-fidelity music for everything you listen to. So you get better sound from smaller, lighter, more comfortable headphones. Volume-optimised EQ boosts highs and low frequencies for consistency of great sound, at whatever volume you listen.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Personalise your audio</strong><br> \nAdjustable EQ allows you to set the bass, mid-range, and treble levels to your personal preferences, or select one of several preset options.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Premium comfort</strong><br>\nThe Quietcomfort QC45 SE offer premium comfort for your listening. Smooth cushions with no pleats, plush synthetic leather and minimal clamping force keep them comfortable over the long listen. Each pivot-point is built with a cast-metal hinge for durability, and a reinforced headband protects against falls.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Clear conversation</strong><br>\nWith a fourth external mic, the Quietcomfort QC45 SE offer improved voice pick-up. They isolate and focus on your voice, while a noise-rejecting algorithm filters out environmental sounds for clearer conversations, even in windy, noisy conditions.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Quickly access your voice assistant</strong><br>\nYou can easily access your phone\'s voice assistant by pressing and holding the multi-function button.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Easy app control</strong><br>\nUse the Bose Music app on your smart device for easy guided set-up and control.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Bluetooth</strong><br>\nConnecting over a stable Bluetooth 5.1 connection, you can pair up to two devices and switch seamlessly between them. And with Bose\'s SimpleSync technology, they pair easily with compatible Bose speakers and soundbars.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Listen longer</strong><br>\nThe Quietcomfort QC45 SE give you up to 24 hours on a single charge. They charge via USB-C in up to 2.5 hours, and a quick 15-minute charge gives you up to 3 hours of play-time. Or you can still plug in with the included audio cable to listen even longer in wired mode.</p>\n\n\n<p><strong>Optimised for Bose SimpleSync</strong><br>\nThis product is optimised for Bose SimpleSync. With SimpleSync technology, you can pair it with selected Bose speakers and soundbars for a personalised listening experience.</p>\n\n</div></div><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"product-description-toggle\" data-testid=\"product:description:showmoreless\" type=\"button\" class=\"button_c-button__pjHF_ button_c-button--tertiary__Nucdh button_c-button--tertiary-icon-right__9Fphk button_c-button--tertiary-icon__5JjQv button_c-button--tertiary-small__GDFL5 button_variant-tonal-dark__O_xhX\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><div class=\"button_icon-container__MTuPR\"><div class=\"button_icon___dtXt\"><img src=\"https://www.jo